here are some key events in the camarena case 
feb 7 1985 drug enforcement administration agent enrique 
camarena is kidnapped outside the us consulate in guadalajara 
march 5 1985 the bodies of camarena and his pilot alfredo 
zavala avelar are found buried at a remote ranch outside 
guadalajara 
april 5 1985 costa rican police officers acting on 
information from us officials capture reputed mexican drug czar 
rafael caro quintero a key suspect in the slayings of camarena and 
zavala caro is returned to mexico 
sept 26 1988 rene verdugo urquidez caros chief lieutenant 
is convicted in los angeles of five counts of conspiracy 
kidnapping murder and two counts of violent acts in support of 
racketeering the two acts were the murders of camarena and zavala 
oct 11 1988 raul lopez alvarez 29 a former guadalajara 
police officer is sentenced in los angeles to 240 years plus life 
for his part in the torture and killings of camarena and zavala 
july 27 1989 juan jose bernaberamirez a police officer from 
the western mexico state of jalisco is arrested in los angeles and 
charged with the murder of a federal agent 
dec 12 1989 caro 37 and ernesto rafael fonesca carrillo 
56 are convicted in mexico and sentenced to 40 years in prison for 
masterminding the killings 
feb 1 1990 miguel aldana ibarra 44 and four others are 
indicted by a federal grand jury in los angeles on charges of 
participating in the 1985 murders 
april 3 1990 dr humberto alvarez machain a guadalajara 
gynecologist is arrested after being abducted and taken to el 
paso texas to face charges he drugged camarena during the agents 
kidnapping torture and murder 
