ecology at the university of florida said the ministers actions 
could set indias efforts to save its royal bengal tiger back 
decades 
its sad what politicians can do to wildlife sunquist said 
in a telephone interview from florida this was a key project 
sunquist who spent a decade studying tigers in southern nepal 
helped start the indian project 
royal bengals account for more than half the worlds estimated 
5000 tigers only the massive siberian tiger which can weigh 800 
pounds and stretch for 10 feet is bigger 
