imprisonment for a july 18 1980 attempt to kill shahpour 
bakhtiar irans prime minister before the 1979 islamic revolution 
a fifth member of the team who did not open fire was sentenced to 
20 years in prison 
bakhtiar escaped injury and still lives in paris where the 
attack occurred but a policeman and a bystander were killed and 
