there are a lot of issues of great concern to many people in public 
life you know im a sitting judge on the 1st circuit and i just 
would be very embarrassed to be asked questions because i could not 
answer them i would not want to put the president or anybody else 
in that position 
rudman said he relayed souters concerns to white house sununu 
who assured him it was not our policy to grill jurists on how 
they would rule on specific issues 
