nabet members at nbc voting in a mail ballot last month and 
this month on the networks latest contract offer rejected it 
1290 to 516 he said 
nbc said in a statement that it would not further revise its 
offer which was changed slightly in april after the union rejected 
it 1601 to 353 
the unions previous contract expired march 30 but its 2373 
members kept working 
