cold coke go to my wife and ask for money and buy us a coke 
she said on the radio the following day he was still asking for 
a coke i told him dont think about it just pray 
the man finally fell silent 
i convinced myself he was not yet dead calabia said i 
told him i would cover his face because rain was dripping down 
