delawarebased dupont pointed to mercks vast international sales 
staff as one reason for hooking up with its new jersey neighbor 
you need to need to introduce the new drug into all the 
major markets of the world simultaneously vagelos said 
the time of exclusivity is limited by patent and competition 
analysts expect more competitors to become allies or partners in 
this highly fragmented field no one player has more than 4 percent 
market share in this 100 billion industry 
but a bullish vagelos predicted that merck will grasp a 
doubledigit world market share by the decades end 
