simultaneously with democrats but details of the package have 
begun to emerge 
the administration proposal would raise the 16cent tax on 
sixpacks of beer to 81 cents and the 3cent levy on the standard 
750 milliliter bottle of wine to 76 cents a gop bargainer said 
the proposal would limit wealthy americans ability to take 
deductions on their federal income tax returns for the state and 
